criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients diagnosed with multiple sclerosis;

          -  patients diagnosed with other neurological diseases (Lateral Amniotrofic Sclerosis ,
             Headache, Parkinson's, Dementia and Epilepsy);

          -  healthy control: blood donors;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  patients diagnosed with other non-neurological diseases;
